@@pSORCERER@@W

Sorcerers are stormbinders and flame-scholars: arcanists who force raw
creation into disciplined patterns of ruin and restoration. Where others study
one school, Sorcerers weaponize breadth.

@@pPassive class advantages@@W
  * @@wSpell critical chance@@W increases with Sorcerer levels
    (+0.1% per level, up to +10% at 100).
  * @@wRemort non-physical damage@@W gains Sorcerer scaling
    (+0.5% per level, up to +50% at 100).
  * @@wArcane healing throughput@@W improves for INT-based arcane healing
    (+2% per Sorcerer level, up to +200% at 100).

@@pUnique Sorcerer mechanics@@W
  * Access to @@wSorcerer stance@@W (dual-cast / no-hit caster posture).
  * Strong synergy with elemental spell ladders and summon-style arcane play.
  * Uses @@wIntelligence@@W as prime remort attribute.

@@pSorcerer reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * @@wWizard + Sorcerer remort reincarnations >= 20@@W unlocks
    @@wEquip Wand@@W permanently.

See also: @@mremort stance wizard grand_magi reincarnate@@W
